<h2 id="2-solution">2. Solution</h2>

<p>We knew the Bacon cipher. 
We created a script to encode this text : 
a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">B</code> for a supper character and a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> lower character.</p>

<p>We obtained :</p>
